# {{ .Name }} ({{ .Type }})

Registers a Docker registry with a Cycloid organization. The registry is the storage backend
that hosts plugin images. Once registered, plugins inside this registry can be declared with
[`cycloid_plugin_registry_plugin`](plugin_registry_plugin) and installed via
[`cycloid_plugin`](plugin).

Set `wait_until_connected = true` to block the apply until the registry reports `connected`
status (up to 5 minutes). Useful in automated pipelines where subsequent steps depend on the
registry being reachable.

